## Luồng hoạt động

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Backend API
    participant JWT as JWT Middleware

    FE->>API: POST /api/auth/login {email, password}
    API->>FE: {user, token}
    Note over FE: Lưu token vào localStorage

    FE->>API: GET /api/applications (+ Bearer token)
    API->>JWT: Kiểm tra token
    JWT->>API: req.user = {id, email, role}
    API->>FE: 200 OK + data

    FE->>API: GET /api/admin/stats (+ Bearer token)
    API->>JWT: Kiểm tra token + role
    JWT->>API: role !== "admin" → 403
    API->>FE: 403 Forbidden

    Note over FE: Token hết hạn sau 7 ngày
    FE->>API: Bất kỳ request + token expired
    API->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
    Note over FE: Auto xóa token, redirect /login
```

